This allows you to select your knowledge about a given word.

Barely is the lowest level and all the words are defaulted to this.

Fairly is the second level of knowledge which means you are gaining better knowledge of a given word.

Nearly is the third level of knowledge which means you are almost there.

Surely is the highest level which means you have gained a complete knowledge of a given word.
